  "Description": {
    "English": "A unique overload to the Multi-Tool's standard mining laser. Beam frequency is modulated precisely in a feedback loop with the delta-waves generated by the impact target.<br><br>Recordings of the target's experiences are thus etched into tiny fragments of metal and rendered as <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Fragmented Qualia</span>. Readability of collected fragments is not guaranteed.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "多用途工具标准开采激光的独特过载。使用撞击目标产生的三角波在反馈回路中精确调制光束频率。<br><br>目标经历的记录就这样被蚀刻成微小的金属碎片，变为<span class=\"name name-stellar\">破碎的感质</span>。无法保证收集的碎片的可读性。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "工具組標準採礦雷射的獨特過載。光束頻率根據發射目標產生的 δ 波經由回饋迴路精準控制。<br><br>目標體驗的紀錄會刻在小塊金屬碎片上作為<span class=\"name name-stellar\">分裂感質</span>。無法保證收集的碎片都能讀取。"
  },
